    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like, the idea of \"fighting\" doesn't even make sense anymore because there's nothing left to fight with. everyone talks about \"hope\" and \"trying new treatments\" but they don't get it. they dont live in this body. do you think it's selfish to just want the suffering to end?",
